Iona Costello and daughter Emily were visiting Manhattan when they went missing on March 30 . 
  Mother and daughter were found safe and well at a hotel on the Upper West Side . 
  They were recognized by the front desk manager of the hotel they were staying at . 
  Iona is in the midst of a legal battle over the will of her late husband who died in 2012 . 
  She and Emily were questioned by police but released on Sunday . 
  The 51-year-old and her daughter were in good health  . 
  Iona's stepson George Costello Jr is in jail in Florida on unrelated charges . 
 